==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cordaitales
<hw>Cordaitales</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>an order of extinct plants
having tall arborescent trunks comparable to or more advanced than
cycads; known from the Pennsylvanian; probably extinct since the
Mesozoic.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> order <ord>Cordaitales</ord>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

